Class LVSFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • system.file.LVSFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class LVSFile
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is an Object Class which holds all the attribute of an LVS File. Including a list holds all the imported file and parameters referencing the displayed actor in VTKPanel.
